Package org.anchoranalysis.plugin.mpp.experiment.bean.objects

Class ExportObjectsAsCroppedImagesTask

Object
AnchorBean<Task<T,​S>>
Task<T,​S>
ExportObjectsBase<MultiInput,​NoSharedState>
ExportObjectsAsCroppedImagesTask
public class ExportObjectsAsCroppedImagesTask
extends ExportObjectsBase<MultiInput,​NoSharedState>
Exports a cropped image for each object-mask showing its context within an image

The context is defined by a bounding-box is placed around an object-mask, and optionally padded.

Author:
Owen Feehan
